{"_id":"0WVnJoWfJXQ8MMt1","name":"Binding of Necrosis","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-ghost-scream-teal.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You unleash a wave of ghastly specters to bind and torment your foes in a 10-foot-cube centered on a point within range.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">When the specters appear, each creature in the area must make a Strength saving throw. A creature takes 7d6 necrotic damage and is restrained on a failure, and takes half as much damage and is not restrained on a success. A creature that starts its turn restrained by the specters takes 3d6 necrotic damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">A creature restrained by the specters can use its action to make a Strength or Dexterity check (its choice) against your spell save DC. On a success, it frees itself.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"cube"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["7d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":"3d6"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":4,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"A Pouch of Ash","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.zm42cDF3XWyZYqXk"}}}
{"name":"Flight of the Dragon","type":"spell","img":"icons/creatures/abilities/wing-batlike-white-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">You whisper ancient arcane words causing draconic wings to sprout from your shoulders. Until the spell ends, you gain the following benefits: </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">• You gain a flying speed of 80 feet for the duration. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">• <strong>Wing Gust.</strong> You may use your bonus action to beat your wings, creating a blast of powerful wind. Each creature within a 10 foot radius must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failure, a creature takes 3d6 bludgeoning and is knocked prone. A creature takes half damage and is not knocked prone on a success. </span><time style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\" datetime=\"2022-03-28T00:31:33.261Z\" aria-label=\"Edited March 28, 2022 10:31 AM\">(edited)</time></p>\n<div tabindex=\"-1\" data-list-item-id=\"chat-messages___chat-messages-957794429853372516\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"Message\" aria-labelledby=\"message-username-957794429853372516 uid_1 message-content-957794429853372516 uid_2 message-timestamp-957794429853372516\">\n<div>\n<div aria-label=\"Message Actions\">\n<div>\n<div tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Add Reaction\" aria-controls=\"popout_43334\" aria-expanded=\"false\"> </div>\n<div tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Reply\"> </div>\n<div tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Create Thread\"> </div>\n<div tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"More\" aria-controls=\"popout_43335\" aria-expanded=\"false\"> </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ol tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Messages in glitter-spell-drafts\" data-list-id=\"chat-messages\">\n<li id=\"chat-messages-957806279403917342\" aria-setsize=\"-1\">\n<div tabindex=\"