{"name":"Curse of Agony","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/skeleton-skull-soul-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You attempt to curse your foe with wracking pain you can see within range. Make a ranged a spell attack at a target creature.  On a hit, the target takes 4d6 necrotic damage and is cursed with agony. On each of your turns for the spells duration, you can use your bonus action to deal 2d6 necrotic damage to the target.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the initial damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["4d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":"2d6"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.i9BdJ7HOOV8FyMdU"}},"_id":"Ym8Y4rF6eNxplDYi"}
{"_id":"gjgf69oz6Bf89euW","name":"Living Dead","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-skeleton-worn-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You raise a small or medium corpse or skeleton as either a @Compendium[dnd5e.monsters.OBujQLLPSmlJiZnL]{Ghoul} or <strong>Dread Warrior</strong> under your control. Any class levels or abilities the creature had in life are gone.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The undead is friendly to you and your companions for the duration. Roll initiative for the creature, which has its own turns. It obeys any verbal commands that you issue to it (no action required by you). If you don't issue any commands to the undead, it defends itself from hostile creatures but otherwise takes no actions.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If your concentration is broken, the undead form breaks apart and the spell immediately ends.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The GM has the Ghoul and Dread Warrior statistics.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"A Piece of Bone or Flesh","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tD9bCP2U7RR7kmos"}}}
{"name":"Shadow Waltz","type":"spell","img":"icons/creatures/claws/claw-talons-glowing-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You slam a talon of violet shadow to harm your foes and whisk you out of reach. Each creature in the 20-foot line must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save a creature takes 3d6 necrotic damage and half as much on a success. Additionally, when you cast this spell you may immediately move 10 feet in a direction you choose. This feature does not provoke attacks of opportunity.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels. </strong>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot above 2nd.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":20,"width":5,"units":"ft","type":"line"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["3d6","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"con","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.PY18wrpjMqd3AWGo"}},"_id":"ngGUE4z3joCThetJ"}
{"name":"Storm Drake's Veil","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-forked-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Lightning bursts forth covering you in a powerful ward of crackling energy, shedding bright light in a 10-foot radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet. You can end the spell early by using an action to dismiss it.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The energy ward gives you resistance to lightning damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You gain 3d8 + 15 hit points in temporary hit points. Until all these temporary hit points are gone, <span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"> </span>whenever a creature within 10 feet of you hits you with a melee attack, the ward lashes with lightning and the attacker takes 2d12 lightning damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, you gain 5 additional Temporary Hit Points for each slot level above 3rd.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["3d8+15","temphp"]],"versatile":"2d12"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"5"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.TxUl4MU50NZOZkFx"}},"_id":"rxr5TBFORTckzsh7"}
{"name":"Arcane Cannon","type":"spell","img":"icons/weapons/artillery/cannon-engraved-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You conjure a cannon of arcane energy in a space within 5 feet of you to crush your foes.</p>\n<p>The cannon has a range of 120 feet, and fires immediately upon summoning. You may spend your bonus action on subsequent turns to cause the cannon to fire again.</p>\n<p>The cannon when fired, targets a point within range you can see and explodes in a 5-foot radius. Any creature within the radius must roll a Dexterity saving throw. On a failure, the creature takes 3d10 force damage and is knocked prone. A creature takes half as much damage and is not knocked prone on a success.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels. </strong>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the cannon deals an additional 1d10 force damage for each slot level above 3rd.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":120,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["3d10","force"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"con","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d10"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.smWFaOENH49LUVL6"}},"_id":"dJm5ELe8Np03bd3P"}
{"name":"Captain's False Coffer","type":"spell","img":"icons/containers/chest/chest-reinforced-steel-pink.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You summon a mimic, which appears in an unoccupied space that you can see within range. The mimic takes on the property of an object you designate, otherwise it resembles a treasure filled chest. The mimic disappears when it drops to 0 hit points or when the spell ends.</p>\n<p>The mimic is friendly to you and your companions for the duration. Roll initiative for the mimic, which has its own turns. It obey any verbal commands that you issue (no action required by you). If you don't issue any commands to it, the mimic defend itself from hostile creatures, but otherwise take no actions.</p>\n<p>The GM has the mimic's statistics.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"con","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.8Ij2nKFS4k6tNzvb"}},"_id":"dDmXnc0r1CADuZT2"}
{"name":"Captain's Orders","type":"spell","img":"icons/equipment/head/hat-tricorn-pirate-black.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You call out commands to help aid your crew in the midst of battle. As an action, you call out to one allied creature within range and give them one of the following orders:</p>\n<p><strong>• Fire!</strong> - The target immediately makes one weapon attack roll at a creature within range, and they gain advantage on their first weapon attack roll on their next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>• Hold Steady! </strong>- The target gains the effects of the Dodge action and gains temporary hit points equal to 1d8+ your spellcasting ability modifier, which lasts till the end of their next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>• Retreat!</strong> - The target can immediately move up to their movement speed without provoking any attacks of opportunity.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"round"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"ally"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"heal","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod","temphp"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7OCoetkuHgJYwfaY"}},"_id":"X1ZsEmyLNbBh6ogN"}
{"name":"Delilah's Alluring Shanty","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-levitate-yellow.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You begin to sing a catchy tune to force a foe and those near them that can hear and see you within range to sing and dance uncontrollably.</p>\n<p>The target, and all those within a 10-foot radius of them must roll a Wisdom saving throw. On a failure, a creature is restrained and suffers disadvantage on ability checks as they begin to dance and sing for the spells duration. A creature with an Intelligence score of 4 or less is unaffected. The initial target also automatically fail any concentration saves they make to maintain a spell while under the effect of this spell, as the shanty ear-worms itself into their head.</p>\n<p>At the end of each of its turns, and each time it takes damage, the target can make another Wisdom saving throw. The target has advantage on the saving throw if it's triggered by damage. On a success, the spell ends.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":10,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":30,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"abil","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.UjTPqkJaHUIAselB"}},"_id":"Mn8O4gakBl49cSVK"}
{"name":"Living Dead","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-skeleton-worn-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You raise a small or medium corpse or skeleton as either a @Compendium[dnd5e.monsters.OBujQLLPSmlJiZnL]{Ghoul} or <strong>Dread Warrior</strong> under your control. Any class levels or abilities the creature had in life are gone.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The undead is friendly to you and your companions for the duration. Roll initiative for the creature, which has its own turns. It obeys any verbal commands that you issue to it (no action required by you). If you don't issue any commands to the undead, it defends itself from hostile creatures but otherwise takes no actions.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">If your concentration is broken, the undead form breaks apart and the spell immediately ends.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">The GM has the Ghoul and Dread Warrior statistics.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"hour"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"touch"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"A Piece of Bone or Flesh","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tD9bCP2U7RR7kmos"}},"_id":"8cTZZb58xAbPWEx2"}
{"name":"Specter's Undertow","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-shadow-monster-purple.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your form turns spectral as you dash through any creatures you can see in a 20-foot-line. Any creature within the line must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failure, a creature takes 4d6 Cold Damage and are stunned until the end of their next turn. A creature takes half damage, and is not stunned on a success.</p>\n<p>You do not provke attacks of opportunity when moving with the spell.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, the damage increases by 1d6 for each slot level above 3rd.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":20,"width":5,"units":"ft","type":"line"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["4d6","cold"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":3,"school":"evo","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"level","formula":"1d6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.9Fg5oQ0aVgyf3tyQ"}},"_id":"kaWGquBZYqZBNlyV"}
{"name":"Weight of Greed","type":"spell","img":"icons/commodities/currency/coin-embossed-skull-gold.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You attempt to enchant your foes into believing they are overburdened with treasure at a point within range you can see.</p>\n<p>Each creature within the 15-foot radius must roll a Wisdom saving throw. On a failure, a creature takes 2d8 psychic damage and their movement is halved for the spells duration. On a success, a creature takes half damage and their movement is not reduced.</p>\n<p>A creature can repeat this saving throw at the end of their turns, ending the spells effect on a success.</p>\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Relics of the Realm","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"minute"},"target":{"value":15,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":"radius"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"wis","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","psychic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":2,"school":"enc","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":true,"ritual":false,"concentration":true},"materials":{"value":"A gold coin","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"none","formula":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"qmZOcULdEoaYH94W":3,"tQqupPK3rQvebWSm":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.DGwUHz2FVdVUpqm7"}},"_id":"EPijCvOnuEVDJUGy"}
